  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK474">
<l>amaintāṅ koḻukā ṉaḷavaṟiyāṉ taṉṉai</l>
<l>viyantāṉ viraintu keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will quickly perish who, ignorant of his own resources flatters himself of his greatness, and does not live in peace with his neighbours.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
